{"metadata": {"page_hash": "74500bbfb9d38c0672822187ec95c9b68ee2328106abf64b59aa5f18c9520488", "original_filename": "aviation_instructors_handbook.pdf", "page_no": 74, "num_pages": 228, "original_width": 612.15997, "original_height": 792.06, "coco_width": 1025, "coco_height": 1025, "collection": "faa_regulations", "doc_category": "laws_and_regulations"}, "form": [{"id_box": 512690, "box": [489.89562278957897, 982.8167478473853, 38.06032678026952, 14.231146535615984], "id_box_line": 44, "box_line": [489.89562278957897, 982.8167478473853, 38.06032678026952, 14.231146535615984], "text": "3-24 ", "category": "Page-footer", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/ABCDEE+Calibri", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512691, "box": [61.5123935660151, 52.620031310759146, 213.5228513063341, 14.378638297603857], "id_box_line": 0, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 52.620031310759146, 213.5228513063341, 14.378638297603857], "text": "Stages of Skill Acquisition ", "category": "Section-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Helvetica,Bold", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512692, "box": [61.5123935660151, 137.99074470368407, 112.40944952673073, 14.27555077898137], "id_box_line": 4, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 137.99074470368407, 112.40944952673073, 14.27555077898137], "text": "Cognitive Stage ", "category": "Section-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman,BoldItalic", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512693, "box": [61.5123935660151, 398.440092290988, 123.48854540423477, 14.275473133348555], "id_box_line": 18, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 398.440092290988, 123.48854540423477, 14.275473133348555], "text": "Associative Stage ", "category": "Section-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman,BoldItalic", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512694, "box": [61.5123935660151, 658.7729714289321, 187.32679629476584, 14.275473133348498], "id_box_line": 32, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 658.7729714289321, 187.32679629476584, 14.275473133348498], "text": "Automatic Response Stage ", "category": "Section-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman,BoldItalic", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512695, "box": [61.5123935660151, 779.848395007954, 900.8422643185897, 72.58958222861904], "id_box_line": 39, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 779.848395007954, 900.5922933020267, 14.27547313334847], "text": "For example, the learner smoothly increases power, adds back pressure on the yoke, and trims the aircraft as a turn is entered. During ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512695, "box": [61.5123935660151, 779.848395007954, 900.8422643185897, 72.58958222861904], "id_box_line": 40, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 794.4333636340681, 900.4985771938009, 14.275473133348498], "text": "the turn, the instructor questions the learner on an unrelated topic. The learner answers the questions, while making two small ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512695, "box": [61.5123935660151, 779.848395007954, 900.8422643185897, 72.58958222861904], "id_box_line": 41, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 809.0054560260586, 900.8422643185897, 14.27547313334847], "text": "adjustments in pitch and trim, and then rolls out of the turn with the altimeter centered on the target altitude. Noting the dramatically ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512695, "box": [61.5123935660151, 779.848395007954, 900.8422643185897, 72.58958222861904], "id_box_line": 42, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 823.5775354771104, 900.4434894689373, 14.27547313334847], "text": "improved performance, the instructor asks \u201cWhat are you doing differently?\u201d The learner seems unsure and says, \u201cI have developed a ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512695, "box": [61.5123935660151, 779.848395007954, 900.8422643185897, 72.58958222861904], "id_box_line": 43, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 838.1625041032245, 77.82063730825126, 14.275473133348498], "text": "feel for it.\u201d$_{ }$", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512696, "box": [61.5123935660151, 677.5114249551801, 900.4589274270904, 87.16167462060957], "id_box_line": 33, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 677.5114249551801, 899.6778203252981, 14.275473133348498], "text": "Automaticity is one of the by-products of practice. As procedures become automatic, less attention is required to carry them out, so it ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512696, "box": [61.5123935660151, 677.5114249551801, 900.4589274270904, 87.16167462060957], "id_box_line": 34, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 692.0835302881095, 900.4589274270904, 14.275447251470837], "text": "is possible to do other things simultaneously, or at least do other things more comfortably. By this stage, learner performance of the ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512696, "box": [61.5123935660151, 677.5114249551801, 900.4589274270904, 87.16167462060957], "id_box_line": 35, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 706.6555967982224, 899.5263709418961, 14.275473133348498], "text": "skill is rapid and smooth. The learner devotes much less deliberate attention to performance, and may be able to carry on a ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512696, "box": [61.5123935660151, 677.5114249551801, 900.4589274270904, 87.16167462060957], "id_box_line": 36, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 721.2405654243365, 899.4755696782981, 14.275473133348498], "text": "conversation or perform other tasks while performing the skill. The learner makes far fewer adjustments during his or her ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512696, "box": [61.5123935660151, 677.5114249551801, 900.4589274270904, 87.16167462060957], "id_box_line": 37, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 735.8126448753882, 899.6261148862772, 14.275473133348498], "text": "performance and these adjustments tend to be small. The learner may no longer be able to remember the individual steps in the ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512696, "box": [61.5123935660151, 677.5114249551801, 900.4589274270904, 87.16167462060957], "id_box_line": 38, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 750.3976264424412, 315.9710839145526, 14.275473133348498], "text": "procedure, or explain how to perform the skill. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512697, "box": [61.5123935660151, 578.0732510794636, 900.6289793826276, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 28, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 578.0732510794636, 900.5090924190941, 14.275473133348498], "text": "For example, Beverly enters the steep turn and again struggles to achieve the desired bank angle. Still working on the bank angle, she ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512697, "box": [61.5123935660151, 578.0732510794636, 900.6289793826276, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 29, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 592.6582326465166, 900.4032201746219, 14.275473133348498], "text": "remembers the persistent altitude control problem and glances at the altimeter. Noticing that the aircraft has descended almost 100 ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512697, "box": [61.5123935660151, 578.0732510794636, 900.6289793826276, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 30, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 607.2302991566296, 900.6289793826276, 14.275473133348441], "text": "feet, she increases back pressure on the control and adjusts the trim slightly. She goes back to a continuing struggle with the bank ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512697, "box": [61.5123935660151, 578.0732510794636, 900.6289793826276, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 31, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 621.8023527258035, 664.3454206095834, 14.275473133348498], "text": "angle, keeping it under control with some effort, and completes the turn 80 feet higher than started. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512698, "box": [61.5123935660151, 504.8275761937226, 900.8224394352344, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 24, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 504.8275761937226, 900.8224394352344, 14.275473133348498], "text": "As the storage of a skill via practice continues, the learner understands how to associate individual steps in performance with likely ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512698, "box": [61.5123935660151, 504.8275761937226, 900.8224394352344, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 25, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 519.3996427038355, 900.4669980299428, 14.275473133348498], "text": "outcomes. The learner no longer performs a series of memorized steps, but is able to assess his or her progress along the way and ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512698, "box": [61.5123935660151, 504.8275761937226, 900.8224394352344, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 26, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 533.9716962730096, 900.6622831773857, 14.275473133348498], "text": "make adjustments in performance. Performing the skill still requires deliberate attention, but the learner is better able to deal with ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512698, "box": [61.5123935660151, 504.8275761937226, 900.8224394352344, 58.004574779688426], "id_box_line": 27, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 548.5566778400625, 85.27900288873838, 14.275473133348441], "text": "distractions. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512699, "box": [61.5123935660151, 417.17858464005246, 900.5754321047813, 72.57664128980127], "id_box_line": 19, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 417.17858464005246, 900.4337779551314, 14.275473133348555], "text": "Even demonstrating how to do something does not result in the learner learning the skill. Practice is necessary in order for the learner ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512699, "box": [61.5123935660151, 417.17858464005246, 900.5754321047813, 72.57664128980127], "id_box_line": 20, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 431.7506382092265, 900.5754321047813, 14.275473133348441], "text": "to learn how to coordinate muscles with visual and tactile senses. Learning to perform various aircraft maintenance skills or flight ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512699, "box": [61.5123935660151, 417.17858464005246, 900.5754321047813, 72.57664128980127], "id_box_line": 21, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 446.3356197762795, 900.4534019106147, 14.275473133348555], "text": "maneuvers requires practice. Another benefit of practice is that as the learner gains proficiency in a skill, verbal instructions become ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512699, "box": [61.5123935660151, 417.17858464005246, 900.5754321047813, 72.57664128980127], "id_box_line": 22, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 460.9076862863924, 900.5536481746756, 14.275473133348555], "text": "more meaningful. A long, detailed explanation is confusing before the learner begins performing, whereas specific comments are ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512699, "box": [61.5123935660151, 417.17858464005246, 900.5754321047813, 72.57664128980127], "id_box_line": 23, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 475.4797527965052, 472.8138067407445, 14.275473133348555], "text": "more meaningful and useful after the skill has been partially mastered. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512700, "box": [61.5123935660151, 332.16959636896183, 900.6255970967849, 43.432469446759114], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 332.16959636896183, 900.6255970967849, 14.275473133348555], "text": "For example, Beverly enters a steep turn after increasing power by a prescribed amount and adjusting the pitch trim. She fixates on ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512700, "box": [61.5123935660151, 332.16959636896183, 900.6255970967849, 43.432469446759114], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 346.74157229250295, 900.4739467855109, 14.275550778981483], "text": "the attitude indicator as she attempts to achieve the desired bank angle. The bank angle exceeds tolerances as she struggles to correct ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512700, "box": [61.5123935660151, 332.16959636896183, 900.6255970967849, 43.432469446759114], "id_box_line": 17, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 361.3265926823725, 259.4409815787203, 14.275473133348441], "text": "it, making many abrupt control inputs. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512701, "box": [61.49573497104033, 244.36535237229498, 900.6356250719889, 72.58947870110853], "id_box_line": 10, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 244.36535237229498, 900.2799676692351, 14.275473133348555], "text": "The best way to prepare the learner to perform a task is to provide a clear, step-by-step example. Having a model to follow permits ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512701, "box": [61.49573497104033, 244.36535237229498, 900.6356250719889, 72.58947870110853], "id_box_line": 11, "box_line": [61.49573497104033, 258.9502951165316, 900.4686205225081, 14.275473133348441], "text": "learners to get a clear picture of each step in the sequence so they understand what is required and how to do it. In flight or ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512701, "box": [61.49573497104033, 244.36535237229498, 900.6356250719889, 72.58947870110853], "id_box_line": 12, "box_line": [61.49573497104033, 273.5222710400727, 900.4902872446885, 14.275550778981255], "text": "maintenance training, the instructor provides the demonstration, emphasizing the steps and techniques. During classroom instruction, ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512701, "box": [61.49573497104033, 244.36535237229498, 900.6356250719889, 72.58947870110853], "id_box_line": 13, "box_line": [61.49573497104033, 288.09441519581844, 900.6356250719889, 14.275473133348441], "text": "an outside expert may be used, either in person or in a video presentation. In any case, learners need to have a clear impression of ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512701, "box": [61.49573497104033, 244.36535237229498, 900.6356250719889, 72.58947870110853], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [61.49573497104033, 302.67935794005496, 135.86911640922878, 14.275473133348555], "text": "what they are to do. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512702, "box": [61.49578520300828, 156.6904918819281, 900.650795126313, 72.61529587404993], "id_box_line": 5, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 156.6904918819281, 900.5555904774366, 14.275473133348441], "text": "Cognitive learning has a basis in factual knowledge. Since the learner has no prior knowledge of flying, the instructor first introduces ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512702, "box": [61.49578520300828, 156.6904918819281, 900.650795126313, 72.61529587404993], "id_box_line": 6, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 171.26248074640796, 900.5636778242784, 14.275550778981483], "text": "him or her to a basic skill. The learner then memorizes the steps required to perform the skill. As the learner carries out these ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512702, "box": [61.49578520300828, 156.6904918819281, 900.650795126313, 72.61529587404993], "id_box_line": 7, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 185.8733183092188, 900.6341867633062, 14.275473133348555], "text": "memorized steps, he or she is often unaware of progress, or may fixate on one aspect of performance. Performing the skill at this ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512702, "box": [61.49578520300828, 156.6904918819281, 900.650795126313, 72.61529587404993], "id_box_line": 8, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 200.45826105345543, 900.3599871941968, 14.275473133348441], "text": "stage typically requires all the learner\u2019s attention; distractions introduced by an instructor often cause performance to deteriorate or ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512702, "box": [61.49578520300828, 156.6904918819281, 900.650795126313, 72.61529587404993], "id_box_line": 9, "box_line": [61.49578520300828, 215.03023697699666, 36.257344056652386, 14.27555077898137], "text": "stop. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512703, "box": [61.5123935660151, 71.68138714238819, 900.5790990384423, 43.43254709239193], "id_box_line": 1, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 71.68138714238819, 900.5472184827764, 14.275550778981255], "text": "Individuals make their way from beginner to expert via three characteristic stages for skill acquisition (or the learning process) as ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512703, "box": [61.5123935660151, 71.68138714238819, 900.5790990384423, 43.43254709239193], "id_box_line": 2, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 86.26631694568573, 900.5790990384423, 14.275550778981597], "text": "follows: cognitive, associative, and automaticity. An instructor needs to recognize each stage in learner performance in order to assess ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}, {"id_box": 512703, "box": [61.5123935660151, 71.68138714238819, 900.5790990384423, 43.43254709239193], "id_box_line": 3, "box_line": [61.5123935660151, 100.83846110143168, 64.95618175588973, 14.275473133348441], "text": "progress. ", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/Times New Roman", "size": 1}}]}